<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WorkIQ Activation Email</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #f4f7f6; /* Changed background color */
            color: #333333; /* Changed text color */
        }
        a { 
            color: #0070f3; /* Changed link color */
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Increased margin */
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff; /* Changed header color */
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 28px; /* Increased font size */
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 20px; /* Increased margin */
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Increased margin */
            text-align: center;
            color: #333333; /* Changed text color */
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555555; /* Changed text color */
        }
        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px; /* Added padding */
            border-radius: 8px; /* Added border radius */
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Added box shadow */
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px; /* Added border radius */
            border-top-right-radius: 8px; /* Added border radius */
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px; /* Added border radius */
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; /* Added border radius */
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Welcome to WorkIQ</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %> ,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with WorkIQ. To activate your account, please use the following code:</p>
            <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
            <p style="text-align: center;">Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you did not register for a WorkIQ account, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:musamuhammedolayinka@gmail.com">Muhammad</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
